title._content: Completed Picture of the Experimental All Aluminum Beer and Soft Drink Can House near Taos, New Mexico. It Took About 70,000 Cans to Complete the Two Story Structure. the Cans Were Laid Horizontally in Two Thicknesses, Separated by a Vertical Sheet of Foa

description._content: Original Caption: Completed Picture of the Experimental All Aluminum Beer and Soft Drink Can House near Taos, New Mexico.
